  "title": "Package Serverless Handlers Using FastAPI with Python 3.12+",
  "summary": "This explainer guides you through the process of creating, testing, and packaging a serverless application using FastAPI and Python 3.12+ for AWS Lambda or other serverless platforms.",
  "key_points": [
    "Understanding the requirements: Python 3.12+, FastAPI, Uvicorn ASGI server, and the target serverless platform (AWS Lambda, Google Cloud Functions, etc.).",
